-- USING UPDATES FOR RPI-64 --

Online updates now available for rpi-64!

Requirements: 
	rpi-64 version 1.2 or higher
Usage:
	sh update
	
if new update package found the following message will occur:
	UPDATES AVAILABLE:
		[number of update] [description]
		...
	Select update number (Q to quit):
	
Select number of update and press enter.

If scripts asks 'Apply update immediately (Y/N)?' and you answers 'y' the update will be applied and script will terminated.
